    $(function(){ 
	    let gender = '${vo.gender}'
	    	if(gender === '남'){
	    		$("input:radio[name='gender'][value='남']").prop("checked", true)
	    	}else if(gender === '여'){
	    		$("input:radio[name='gender'][value='여']").prop("checked", true)
	    	}
    })
